{"tid":2405234,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜素顏出鏡向fans拜年 《驅魔麵館》金世正甜笑送祝福","createTime":"2021-02-12T07:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T08:40:14.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9ae57741f35603943eca9e3102b9ceadaa20f5e1","tid":2405234,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KYIuWptGJs9pWhNwBODIjDGdb7Q=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4VKLFF363JF7TKO7MU5FRXOQVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKYIuWptGJs9pWhNwBODIjDGdb7Q%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4VKLFF363JF7TKO7MU5FRXOQVQ.jpg&h=2e995356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日是大年初一，不少藝人都透過IG向fans送上新年祝福，當中包括女團TWICE的台灣成員周子瑜及憑人氣劇《驅魔麵館》爆紅的金世正。<br />\n<br />\n未知是否受武漢肺炎影響，導致子瑜今年未能回台灣跟家人一起過年，不過她昨晚就特地在TWICE的官方IG上載靚靚自拍照，提早跟fans拜年：「大家開心過春年。」相中子瑜似乎以素顏出鏡，但皮膚仍然白滑，少了濃妝的亮麗卻顯得更清純。至於金世正就手持着可愛卡通造型的牛牛揮春，在鏡頭前大晒甜美笑容，獲fans大讚靚女。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LTM_3tACS2QzDnHMOYANRDGjml0=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QXCP6KNWCFBD7PGIGRIYOU73K4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLTM_3tACS2QzDnHMOYANRDGjml0%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQXCP6KNWCFBD7PGIGRIYOU73K4.jpg&h=92c2d740&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pgaOnQT6ATkRJO3Wxc1tAZSnpqQ=/802x920/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YQRIXQ37UBHEDLCIJKQHZBO53A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpgaOnQT6ATkRJO3Wxc1tAZSnpqQ%3D%2F802x920%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfro